Package: LPWC
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Lag Penalized Weighted Correlation for Time Series Clustering
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Thevaa", family = "Chandereng", role =
        c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "chandereng@wisc.edu", comment
        = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4078-9176")), person(given = "Anthony",
        family = "Gitter", role = c("aut", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID =
        "0000-0002-5324-9833")))
Description: Computes a time series distance measure for clustering
        based on weighted correlation and introduction of lags. The
        lags capture delayed responses in a time series dataset. The
        timepoints must be specified. T. Chandereng, A. Gitter (2020)
        <doi:10.1186/s12859-019-3324-1>.
